quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  4,1,"Adasamma, monsuro mo Wura Nyankopֽ»n no a ֶ†bֽ»ֽ» mo firi honam baako mu, na ֶ†bֽ»ֽ» ne yere nso firii (honam korֽ» no ara) mu, na Wג€™ama mmarima pii ne mmaa (ase atr־µ) afiri wֽ»n mmienu no mu; na monsuro Nyankopֽ»n no a mode no bisa (anaa mode no srֹ›); na (mony־µ ahw־µ yie wֽ») abusua ho, efiris־µ Nyankopֽ»n de־µ ֶ†rew־µn mo"
  4,2,"Monfa nyanka no nso sika (anaa agyapade־µ) ma wֽ»n. Na monhw־µ na moanfa de־µ ־µny־µ ansesa de־µ ־µy־µ, na monhw־µ na moanfa wֽ»n agyapade־µ anka mo agyapade־µ ho ammֽ» mu anni. Nokor־µ s־µ ־µno y־µ bֽ»ne k־µse־µ paa"
  4,3,"S־µ mosuro s־µ montumi ny־µ (biribiara) p־µp־µ־µp־µ mma nyanka no a, ־µne־µ monware mmaa no de־µ ־µy־µ anisֽ» ma mo; mmienu, mmi־µnsa ne ־µnnan. Nas־µ mosuro s־µ montumi ny־µ (biribiara) p־µp־µ־µp־µ wֽ» mmaa no nt־µm a, ־µne־µ (monware) baako, anaas־µ (monware nneduafoֽ» mmaa no a), wֽ»n wֽ» monsa mu a wֽ»ג€™y־µ modea no bi; ־µno mmom na ־µy־µ, s־µde־µ monnkֽ» fom"
  4,4,"Na monfri akoma pa mu mfa mmaa no (awade־µ ho) tiri aseda a ־µy־µ aky־µde־µ no ma wֽ»n. Nas־µ wֽ»n ara de wֽ»n p־µ mu ma mo emu biribi a, ־µne־µ monfa anigye־µ ne ahos־µp־µ nni"
  4,5,"Na Monhw־µ na moanfa wֽ»n a wֽ»n adwen nyinnii־µ no sika (anaa agyapade־µ) a Nyankopֽ»n de abֽ» mo dwetire no annhy־µ wֽ»n nsa; na emu na momֽ» wֽ»n akֽ»nhoma, na monfira wֽ»n ntoma, na monka kasa pa (a abodwe־µ wֽ» mu) nkyer־µ wֽ»n"
  4,6,"Na monsc nyanka no nhwj nkcsi sj wcג€™bjduru awadej soc. Nasj mohunu sj wcn adwene anyin a jnej monfa wcn sika ( anaa agyapadej ) no nhyj wcn nsa. Na monhwj na moanni no wc kwan bcne ne ntjmtjm so ( amma ankcba sj ) wcג€™bjnyini no ( na agyapadej no asa ). Na obia ne nsamu yj no, wcmc mmcden sj wc bjhyj ne ho so ( wc agyanka sika die no ho ), na obi a ahia no no nso (sj wcredi bi a) wc ni no kwan pa so. Nasj mode wcn sika (anaa agyapadej) no rehyj wcn nsa a, moma adansefoc mjdi wcn ho adansej. Na Nyankopcn som bo wc akontabuo mu"
